              <h3>Web Development</h3>
              <p>
                Students will learn relevant and current web technologies
                including HTML5, CSS3, Javascript, PHP, MySQL, popular content
                management systems and web frameworks. Other topics include
                mobile web application development, responsive design,
                accessibility, and user-centered design.
              </p>
